dc_title_s: The world on Mercator projection: prepared expressly for Kiggins & Tooker Co
dc_description_s: George F. Cram Company. North Decimal Degree 80.000000. South Decimal Degree -70.000. East Decimal Degree 90.000. West Decimal Degree -90.000. Map is color coded to indicate colonial possessions and spheres of political influence. Map shows steam boat trans-oceanic routes, and routes of submarine cable lines. Data on the dimensions of the earth and continents.
